		<div id="comment_body_64410384"><p>The current version is Tesla FSD is a much better driver than most people.<br>We need to come to terms with the fact that self driving cars are (or will be) better drivers than most people on the road who are easily distracted, don't stay between the lines, drive drunk, don't do a full stop at stop signs and run into the car in front of them.<br>Yesterday I drove 70 miles on a combination of local roads, secondary highways and divided highway using Tesla FSD. The performed flawlessly. It stopped at signs and lights<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64410384">

